title: VH1 100 Greatest Hard Rock Songs
description: Another "Greatest List" from the madmen at VH1. 100 hard rock songs handpicked by VH1 viewers, and presented this last week on VH1. While I don't personally agree with the list, it does contain some magical ditties. Let it be a starting point for discussion for your own 100 greatest. Please seed when finished, share the love. And remember.... Kick Out The Jams Motherfucker!!
